[docs]class MethodStrategyFactoryInterface(ABC):
    @abstractmethod
    def create(self):
        raise NotImplementedError

    @abstractmethod
    def get_strategies(self):
        raise NotImplementedError




[docs]class DefaultMethodStrategyFactory(MethodStrategyFactoryInterface):
    def create(self):
        return {s.name: s for s in self.get_strategies()}

    def get_strategies(self):
